text:
[Verse]
Stars shine up above
We fall in love tonight
Moonlight's taking over
Hearts feel so light

[Verse 2]
Feet on the grass
Time starts to fly
Magic in our steps
We dance and sigh

[Chorus]
Moonlit dance
Hands close tight
Dreams start now
Under the night

[Verse 3]
Lights in the sky
Whispers all around
Lost in this moment
Never coming down

[Verse 4]
Rhythm so sweet
Laughter in the air
Twirl through the darkness
We don't have a care

[Chorus]
Moonlit dance
Hands close tight
Dreams start now
Under the night
title: Moonlit Dance
